🔥 Aquaman ★ Before And After


Aquaman ★ Before And After, Then and now.
 Mashup about new DC comics movie "Aquaman ". How members of the cast has changed through the years, funny moments, funny edits, everything is here. I hope you like it, even if you're marvel fan :), and please give me a comment. Enjoy!

Main Cast:

Jason Momoa as Aquaman / Arthur Curry
Amber Heard as Mera
Willem Dafoe as Vulko
Patrick Wilson as King Orm
Dolph Lundgren as King Nereus
Nicole Kidman as Atlanna
Yahya Abdul-Mateen II as Manta
